      </memberdef>
    </sectiondef>
    <briefdescription>
<para>IEEE 802.15.4 net management library. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="since"><para>1.0 </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="version"><para>0.8.0</para>
</simplesect>
</para>
<para>The IEEE 802.15.4 net management library provides runtime configuration features that applications can interface with directly.</para>
<para>Most of these commands are also accessible via shell commands. See the shell&apos;s help feature (<computeroutput>shell&gt; ieee802154 help</computeroutput>).</para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>All section, table and figure references are to the IEEE 802.15.4-2020 standard. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
